<br>
Darkrayne, you may rest assured that I will neither hide in Ambassador Vresk's shadow nor clink to the tassels of his robe.  My life in the past has indeed been muddled and, on occasion, directionless.  I retreated from my Hatred in fear, having seen what unmastered Hatred (not to mention raw ambition and hubris) did to Tier'Dal I considered noble and exemplary.  Your concerns about my character and commitment are understandable, but groundless.  My experience has taught me to embrace the Hatred that burns within me.  Yet I have also witnessed the folly of allowing that flame to consume me.<br>
<br>
During my brief sojourn in another place, far from Norrath, I observed another powerful tool.  It consisted of a focused, concentrated ray of light.  The people of that place called this a Laser.  Few substances could withstand its terrible heat.  I believe our Hatred must become like this Laser, so devastating in its focus and concentration that no obstacle shall prevent us from subjugating all the races of Norrath and Luclin.  I also believe that if we do not begin applying the discipline to do this, our Hatred will destroy us rather than our enemies.  Who can imagine the torments our Father has in store if we should fail Him in this fashion?<br>
<br>
<br>
Tesarra the Necromancer<br>
Neriak, Brell Serilis <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/ukhasirath.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Khasirath</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.violentharvest.com/sigs/vh_anim.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Reaper of the Harvest</span><br>  Posts: 573<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/26/02 8:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/fvhbrellfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=170.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.columbus.rr.com/harvest/khassmall.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Petition for Entrance</span><hr size=1> *bows*<br>
<br>
Well met, Tessera. You are not the first Teir'Dal I have known who has strayed into confusion, and turned from the Father. It takes great strength and sacrifice to return to His Path. I pray ye are strong enough, but I am sure that the legendary Obsidian Blade saw to it that you are.<br>
<br>
And as to your words about Hate, and how it can consume the undisciplined... I have always agreed on this. I do not know of the 'laser' you mentioned, but I know that Hate is a powerful tool. Unfocussed it can destroy all around it. We all seek to focus our Hate into a weapon of the Father's Will. Only in this fashion can we truly serve Him.<br>
<br>
As our motto states, Hate with Honor. Hate is first always, but we must have the Honor and the focus to direct it, lest we be consumed.<br>
<br>
I pray we meet soon within the lands of Norrath.<br>
<br>
The Reaper, Khasirath S`Therik<br>
